            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JH">
                <p>Sacred to the gods of the underworld. (...)ntelus Seleucus...(lived for) 13 years and 8 months, P(ublius)...ntelus Seleucus his father...for his dutiful...(?) and for Simbolicus (?)... his grandson, who lived for 16 years and 7 months</p>
